text: Gwen Nagel (20 May 1946 – 17 October 2009) was an international cricket umpire. She has umpired in one Women's Test Match and three Women's One Day Internationals. She has played 14 First class matches for North Shore Women. She was a right-handed batsman and bowled left-arm medium fast. ==References== Category:New Zealand women cricketers Category:New Zealand sportswomen Category:New Zealand cricket umpires Category:1946 births Category:2009 deaths
